# Five style of scalars

plain: this is subject to implicit typing
single: 'won''t be subject to implicit typing'
double: "can contain \"Any Value\" \n\x7c\u206e"
literal: |
    \  /   /\    |\    /| |
     \/   /  \   | \  / | |
     |   /----\  |  \/  | |
     |  /      \ |      | |____
folded: >
  Kinda like html where newlines
  become spaces.

